16-Hole Titanium Nail Head for 16mm Coil

  • Fits all the dabbing specialists Nail Bodies, P/N 3101, 3102, 3201, and all nail bodies with 5/16-18" threaded connection
  • Material: Grade 2 Titanium 99.4% Pure, Melted in the USA
  • Engineered, Designed, & CNC Machined in the USA

  • The Bowl is Designed to not “Never Lose a Dab”, with no holes in the bottom

*Engineered to use at a coil temperature setting of 800 degrees Fahrenheit.
